}

package 2
class family{
car="i am your little brother I am ussing your car today forgive if i destroy it"
}

if we do not specify any modifiers default behaviour will assign to our variable
and methods and they will only be avaiblable within the same package.
public:
    if we declare our methods or instance variables we can access
    them from anywhere; any package,or any class.

